Problem Statement :Find the sum of all elements in an array. 
                   Example, Input: {2, 5, 1, 3, 0}
                            Output: 11
Approach (Brute force). Sort the array in ascending order and check every element to sort to get the second smallest and largest number. 

public class ArraySum {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] arr = {2, 5, 1, 3, 0}; 
        int sum = 0; 

        for (int num : arr) {
            sum += num; 
        }

        System.out.println("Sum of all elements: " + sum);
    }
}
